:R-HSA-1251932  a           owl:NamedIndividual , obo:GO_0008150 ;
        rdfs:comment        "Activation of PLCG1 signaling is observed only in the presence of ERBB2:EGFR heterodimers, with PLCG1 binding to phosphorylated tyrosine Y992 and Y1173 in the C-tail of EGFR (Chattopadhyay et al. 1999), and potentially Y1023 in the C-tail of ERBB2 (Fazioli et al. 1991, Cohen et al. 1996)." ;
        rdfs:label          "PLCG1 events in ERBB2 signaling" ;
